additionalProperty.name: Contains
additionalProperty.value: Contains isopropyl alcohol as a preservative. Contains benzoates.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Do not use Voltaren Emulgel: - On children under 12 years. - If you are pregnant or breastfeeding. - If you are allergic to diclofenac, aspirin, any other anti-inflammatory medicines of pain relievers. - If tube seal is broken or missing. Stop use and see your doctor immediately if: - You experience an allergic reaction. While using this product: - Unless a doctor or pharmacist has told you to, do not use this product with other medicines that you are taking regularly. - Avoid contact with eyes.
